# ION DEX Visual Quality Standards — Mandatory

Reference quality: crisp, bright glass cards with clearly visible rounded corners, neon rim, and readable text. NO muddy/dark/blurry glass.

## Border & Corner Rules
- ALL cards: `border-radius: 1.5rem` minimum (24px)
- Outer frame: `border-radius: 2rem`
- Neon rim: `inset: -2px`, `border-radius: inherit`, ALWAYS paired with visible `box-shadow`
- Inner card: `border-radius: calc(2rem - 1px)`

## Glass Specifications (exact values — DO NOT CHANGE)
```css
background-color: rgba(6, 16, 36, 0.3);
backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(1.35);
box-shadow:
  inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.22),   /* top highlight */
  0 0 56px rgba(36,247,255,0.18),           /* cyan outer glow */
  0 0 42px rgba(255,59,212,0.12);           /* magenta outer glow */
```

## Color Palette (EXACT hex, no deviation)
| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| cyan-neon | #24f7ff | Borders, glows, highlighted data |
| magenta | #ff3bd4 | Secondary glow, accents |
| glass-bg | rgba(6,16,36,0.3) | Card backgrounds |
| text-primary | #e0f0ff | Headers and key labels |
| text-secondary | #8ab4d8 | Body text |
| text-dim | #5a7a9a | Subdued labels |

## Anti-Patterns (NEVER)
- `background-blend-mode: overlay` on glass cards
- `background-color alpha > 0.45` — blocks aurora
- `backdrop-filter: none` — kills glass effect
- `blur < 12px` — too noisy
- `blur > 20px` — too muddy (Master says "模糊不清")
- Text color `#6b7280` or similar gray — use `#8ab4d8` min
- Sharp corners (`border-radius < 1rem`) on any card surface
- Dark backgrounds (`rgba(r,g,b, >0.5)`) on cards
